content.comment:
We thank all reviewers for your reviews. We have updated the paper and the changes are in blue for easier reference. To summarize, we have added:
  1) visualization of attention and qualitative examples;
  2) additional analysis on conditional masking vs. joint random masking;
  3) more recent SOTA on VCR and NLVR2;
  4) additional experiments on Conceptual-Caption-only pre-training;
  5) some revisions suggested by the reviewers.

